{"tid":845640,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 洪欣深夜發文：打女人的男人要不得","createTime":"2018-10-02T23:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T03:30:37.000Z","uid":48905,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8f2e5454efd071090aa9647991104ad6d2c196ff","tid":845640,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T23:36:11.000Z","msg":"早前藝人洪欣老公張丹峰傳出偷食索爆經理人嘅新聞，消息震撼全城，最後經各方出面澄清，事件告一段落。早兩日洪欣喺微博發放同老公一齊做嘢嘅相大晒恩愛，點知尋晚洪欣突然喺微博留言：「打女人的男人要不得。」瞬即令人懷疑發生家暴，唔少網民都留言話好擔心佢嘅情況，有網民覺得係帳號被盜，亦有網民推測佢係講緊其他人都唔定。而洪欣身邊嘅工作人員表示，因為佢哋習慣早瞓，依家未聯絡到問清楚情況，不過工作人員相信佢哋感情冇問題。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/073534_f39e943a588b68532fd547acf332f9d5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F073534_f39e943a588b68532fd547acf332f9d5.png&h=968702b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76e922b544de1caf1bfdac301e12daf02c07ac00","tid":845640,"uid":48905,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T23:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/012045_9303f3c93486997d3fe247b1a80999d4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F012045_9303f3c93486997d3fe247b1a80999d4.gif&h=74a0e790&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf0af3a363a66824275818a7cd358b53f9218e62","tid":845640,"uid":48905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/092732_2371cc71bc9517974704c7f22624f5e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F092732_2371cc71bc9517974704c7f22624f5e5.png&h=99fbf49a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a192cf448ca5b84ba5d3c22137c691980ac5bf1a","tid":845640,"uid":48905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/092802_7f4